title: Unboxing DJI’s £415 Osmo Action 6 Action Camera

description:
XPeng’s new humanoid robot, IRON, went viral after the company cut it open on stage to prove it wasn’t a human in disguise. But what does IRON look like up close? Mashable reporter Amanda Yeo got rare access to a private demo, where she saw IRON’s soft skin, humanlike proportions, and fully autonomous movement firsthand.
